      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's just what people say to feel better, but it's not true. hope is just a chemical reaction to avoid the reality of it all. there's no \"getting better\" in a universe that's just fundamentally indifferent. everything we do is just making noise in a vacuum. it doesn't actually change the outcome.",
